If you are a big fan of Sanrio characters, listen up! 
Sanrio Character Ranking 2020 is going on now. So how do you cast your vote on your favourite character? 
Just simply select the character in this game & collect as many letters as possible (the more letters you get, the higher the votes are!) Head over to https://bit.ly/rankinggame & try out this game today! #bryxadv
Love hello kitty ❤️ you’re so cute!
